Package game

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Application
    The main class for the Jurassic World game.
    CorpseFactory
    Creates a new corpse dependent on Dinosaur Species
    Counter
    Implements a counter class
    DinosaurHold
    Implements a class which holds all the dinosaur objects in the world
    EcoHold
    Implements a class which holds all the ecopoint objects of all players
    Ecopoints
    Implementing a currency system (eco points) in the game world
    FindNearestLocation
    Implements a class that determines the closest actor and closest location
    GameDriver
    Runs the Jurassic World game and allows the player to choose different game modes
    LaserGun
    Implements a laser gun weapon item
    MapHolder
    Implements a class that holds a list of GameMaps available in the world
    MapSwitch
    Implements a class which adds an edge capability to top/bottom ground objects
    Player
    Class representing the Player.
    PortableItem
    Base class for any item that can be picked up and dropped.
    Sky
    Implements sky static class for game world
    Testing  
    VendingItemFactory
    A factory class that creates instances of each vending machine item.
    VendingMachine
    Implements a Vending Machine class object that extends from Ground
